      { time: '5:00 PM', name: 'Turkish Airlines CIP Lounge at IST', note: 'One of the finest airport lounges in the world: full hot Turkish buffet, spa with showers, sleeping pods, golf simulator, cinema. A perfect final hour before the long flight home. Ask at check-in whether your ticket includes lounge access.', tip: 'Ask at check-in about CIP lounge access — always worth requesting' },
